---
import Container from './Container.astro';
---

<div class="relative" id="home">
  <div
    aria-hidden="true"
    class="absolute inset-0 grid grid-cols-2 -space-x-52 opacity-40">
    <div class="blur-[106px] h-56 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary to-purple-400">
    </div>
    <div class="blur-[106px] h-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-400 to-sky-300">
    </div>
  </div>
  <Container>
    <div class="relative pt-36 ml-auto">
      <div class="lg:w-2/3 text-center mx-auto">
        <h1
          class="text-gray-900 flex lg:w-full flex-col dark:text-white font-bold text-5xl md:text-6xl xl:text-7xl">
          <span class="text-primary lg:w-full dark:text-white">
            Hi, I'm Ezgi,
          </span>
          <span class="text-2xl w-full dark:text-white">
            Student at Ko√ß University..
          </span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-8 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          I am doing a double major with Chemistry and Computer Engineering .
        </p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          I am in my sophomore year.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="my-16 flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-y-4 gap-x-6">
        <a
          href="mailto:eakkaya21@ku.edu.tr"
          class="relative flex h-11 w-full items-center justify-center px-6 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:rounded-full before:bg-primary before:transition before:duration-300 hover:before:scale-105 active:duration-75 active:before:scale-95 sm:w-max">
          <span class="relative text-base font-semibold text-white">
            Email Me
          </span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://github.com/ezgiakkaya"
          class="relative flex h-11 w-full items-center justify-center px-6 before:absolute before:inset-0 before:rounded-full before:border before:border-transparent before:bg-primary/10 before:bg-gradient-to-b before:transition before:duration-300 hover:before:scale-105 active:duration-75 active:before:scale-95 dark:before:border-gray-700 dark:before:bg-gray-800 sm:w-max">
          <span
            class="relative text-base font-semibold text-primary dark:text-white">
            Go to Github
          </span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-1">
      <a
        href="https://www.ku.edu.tr/en/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <div
          class="p-4 grayscale flex flex-col items-center justify-center transition duration-200 hover:grayscale-0">
          <img
            src="./koc-university.png"
            class="h-12 w-auto mx-auto"
            loading="lazy"
            alt="client logo"
            width=""
            height=""
          />
          <p class="flex-col items-center mt-8 justify-center w-fit">
            Visit Koc University
          </p>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>
  </Container>
  <Container class="mt-0">
    <svg
      xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
      viewBox="0 0 24 24"
      fill="currentColor"
      class="w-6 h-6 text-secondary">
      <path
        fill-rule="evenodd"
        d="M9 4.5a.75.75 0 01.721.544l.813 2.846a3.75 3.75 0 002.576 2.576l2.846.813a.75.75 0 010 1.442l-2.846.813a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576 2.576l-.813 2.846a.75.75 0 01-1.442 0l-.813-2.846a3.75 3.75 0 00-2.576-2.576l-2.846-.813a.75.75 0 010-1.442l2.846-.813A3.75 3.75 0 007.466 7.89l.813-2.846A.75.75 0 019 4.5zM18 1.5a.75.75 0 01.728.568l.258 1.036c.236.94.97 1.674 1.91 1.91l1.036.258a.75.75 0 010 1.456l-1.036.258c-.94.236-1.674.97-1.91 1.91l-.258 1.036a.75.75 0 01-1.456 0l-.258-1.036a2.625 2.625 0 00-1.91-1.91l-1.036-.258a.75.75 0 010-1.456l1.036-.258a2.625 2.625 0 001.91-1.91l.258-1.036A.75.75 0 0118 1.5zM16.5 15a.75.75 0 01.712.513l.394 1.183c.15.447.5.799.948.948l1.183.395a.75.75 0 010 1.422l-1.183.395c-.447.15-.799.5-.948.948l-.395 1.183a.75.75 0 01-1.422 0l-.395-1.183a1.5 1.5 0 00-.948-.948l-1.183-.395a.75.75 0 010-1.422l1.183-.395c.447-.15.799-.5.948-.948l.395-1.183A.75.75 0 0116.5 15z"
        clip-rule="evenodd">
      </path>
    </svg>
    <h2
      class="my-8 text-2xl font-bold text-primary dark:text-white md:text-4xl">
      Interests
    </h2>

    <!-- *** INTERESTS *** -->
    <div
      class="mt-16 grid divide-x divide-y divide-gray-100 dark:divide-gray-700 overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-gray-100 text-gray-600 dark:border-gray-700 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 lg:divide-y-0 xl:grid-cols-3">
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <img
            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/4341/4341139.png"
            class="w-12"
            width="512"
            height="512"
            alt="burger illustration"
          />

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary">
              Design and Development
            </h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              I have always had a passion for creativity and self-expression,
              which led me to start painting at a young age. As I grew older, my
              interests expanded to include the digital world, and I began
              exploring web development as a means of harnessing my creativity
              in new and exciting ways. While the mediums may be different, the
              drive to create and express myself through art has remained a
              constant source of inspiration and motivation for me. Whether I am
              working on a new website or creating a painting, I always strive
              to bring my unique perspective and creative vision to the task at
              hand.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <img
            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/4341/4341134.png"
            class="w-12"
            width="512"
            height="512"
            alt="burger illustration"
          />

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary">
              Photography
            </h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              As I journeyed to new and exciting destinations, I found myself
              increasingly drawn to capturing the beauty and diversity of the
              world through the lens of my camera. It allows me to explore my
              creativity in new ways, and the process of developing my own
              photos has been a rewarding and fulfilling experience. With every
              click of the shutter, I strive to capture the unique spirit and
              essence of the places I visit and the people I meet."
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="group relative bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 transition hover:z-[1] hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-gray-600/10">
        <div class="relative space-y-8 py-12 p-8">
          <img
            src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/4341/4341160.png"
            class="w-12"
            width="512"
            height="512"
            alt="burger illustration"
          />

          <div class="space-y-2">
            <h5
              class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white transition group-hover:text-secondary">
              Computational Chemistry
            </h5>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
              The field of chemistry is rapidly evolving, with an increasing
              focus on data-driven and computational approaches to research. My
              research is dedicated to exploring the intricate details of
              molecular interactions, using a variety of computational methods
              such as molecular docking and machine learning to predict these
              interactions.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- *** INTERESTS END *** -->
  </Container>
</div>
